0031 REM "20Aug96 WGH: Re-initialize Totals for each item (1235)"
0032 REM "26Aug96 WGH: Open IVM-14 for item synonym lookup (110,130,170)"
0033 REM "12Feb97 WGH: Year incorrectly labeled when non-calendar fiscal year (555)"
